9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/984800/extras/3437fea325cd8f3c159be405131eb644.mp4?t=1761824259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Mod Support: </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think you could bring some more pizazz to the table? GREAT! Step on up to the plate and create your own ingredients, recipes and scenario levels via Steam Workshop!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/984800/extras/aae1e6c20ade4bc3a6feffdcc4c3ffe2.poster.avif?t=1761824259\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/984800/extras/aae1e6c20ade4bc3a6feffdcc4c3ffe2.webm?t=1761824259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/984800/extras/aae1e6c20ade4bc3a6feffdcc4c3ffe2.mp4?t=1761824259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
